  2286→/* ----------------------- REPLICATION SCRIPT CACHE --------------------------
  2287→ * The goal of this code is to keep track of scripts already sent to every
  2288→ * connected slave, in order to be able to replicate EVALSHA as it is without
  2289→ * translating it to EVAL every time it is possible.
  2290→ *
